  "body": "**Describe the bug**\r\n\r\nRight now we use `WeakMap` to cache message id and it takes time to cache messages there\r\n\r\n<img width=\"1233\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2022-03-07 at 13 48 33\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/10568965/156984276-5ca14d5b-21e2-4422-affa-6166e3f34256.png\">\r\n\r\nIt seems that after we improve the memory, this map keeps growing and we don't control the max size of it\r\n\r\n**Expected behavior**\r\n\r\nFind another way to cache that we can control the size of the map",
